{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0006","text":"一句爲什麼不找找你","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","疑問","傷害"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["爲什麼","找找你","傷害"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,2,3,3,9,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jat1","geoi3","sam6","mo1","bat1","zaau2","zaau2","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"一句","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"爲什麼","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"找","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"找","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"以疑問句表達對對方行為的困惑，暗示對方找尋自己是為了傷害。"},"source":{"title":"必殺技","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1247","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0007","text":"我練到 再倔強 再絕也 也永沒法比","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","無力感","差距"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["倔強","絕","沒法比"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,4,4,2,0,4,2,5,5,5,2,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","lin6","dou3","zoi3","gwat6","koeng4","zoi3","zyut6","jaa5","jaa5","wing5","mut6","faat3","bei2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我練","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"到","pos":"PART"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"倔強","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"再絕","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"永","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"沒法","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"比","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"描述自己變得多麼堅強或絕望，都無法與對方抗衡。"},"source":{"title":"必殺技","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1247","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0008","text":"求你別要 如從前 純熟地碰我","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","懇求","傷害"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["求","別要","純熟","碰我"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,2,4,0,0,0,0,2,2,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["kau4","nei5","bit6","jiu3","jyu4","cung4","cin4","seon4","suk6","dei6","pung3","ngo5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"求","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"別要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"從前","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"純熟","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"地","pos":"PART"},{"text":"碰","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"直接懇求對方不要再用過去那種熟練的方式來傷害自己。"},"source":{"title":"必殺技","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1247","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0009","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0009","text":"(求你別說 仍能如 良朋地對我)","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","懇求","友情"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["別說","良朋","對我"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,4,0,0,0,0,0,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","bit6","syut3","jing4","nang4","jyu4","loeng4","pang4","dei6","deoi3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"求","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"別說","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"仍能","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"良朋","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"地","pos":"PART"},{"text":"對","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"}],"syntax_notes":"括號內是另一種懇求，希望對方不要再以朋友的姿態對待自己。"},"source":{"title":"必殺技","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1247","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0010","text":"而我問我 爲何還 能夠碰傷我","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","自省","痛苦"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["問我","爲何","碰傷我"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,2,5,0,0,0,4,4,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ji4","ngo5","man6","ngo5","ho4","waan4","nang4","gau3","pung3","soeng1","ngo5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"問","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"爲何","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"還","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"能夠","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"碰傷","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"自問為何即使分手了，仍然會因為對方而受到傷害。"},"source":{"title":"必殺技","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1247","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0011","text":"(而我問我 爲何還 能對得起我)","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","自省","愧疚"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["問我","爲何","對得起我"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,5,0,0,0,4,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","man6","ngo5","ho4","waan4","nang4","deoi3","dak1","hei2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"問","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"爲何","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"還","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"對得起","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"}],"syntax_notes":"括號內是另一種自問，反思自己是否對得起這段關係或對方。"},"source":{"title":"必殺技","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1247","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MTI0Nw_0012","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
